b'existen distintos tipos de trastorno bipolar. estos pueden consistir en man\xc3\xada o hipoman\xc3\xada y depresi\xc3\xb3n. los s\xc3\xadntomas pueden causar cambios impredecibles en el estado de \xc3\xa1nimo y el comportamiento, lo cual da como resultado un gran sufrimiento e importantes dificultades en la vida'

bipolar 2 : it is just depressive episodes.

b'@relativni1 @shattered6moon @wishuwerenone as someone who has both bpd and bipolar the length of the episode is what determines the difference. bipolar episodes last at least 1 week for mania and 2 for depression, whereas swings with bpd happen over the course of minutes/hours/days'

b'@zkat__ bipolar is more than shifts in self-image: periods of mania often include extreme energy and lack of inhibition/judgment.

what you\xe2\x80\x99re describing is pretty common across mental health scenarios. it is likely a hurt \xe2\x80\x9cpart\xe2\x80\x9d of your psyche getting activated.

can say more if wanted.'
